<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1674316-hi-everyone-i-found-out-that-there-were-2">Hi everyone. I found out that there were 2 versions of the book, one with 12 chapters and the other one 14 chapters. Is there any significant difference between the two?</a>
