<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">In my version it has 12 chapters with two apendix chapters, the two other chapters are there two explain the political situation, with little or o nar<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">In my version it has 12 chapters with two apendix chapters, the two other chapters are there two explain the political situation, with little or o narrative, they serve to explain the complex political situation within Catalonia and the situation of Orwell's POUM comrades<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
