        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer156502407" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15319210063574811891">A wonderful book full of the stink and horror of war. The accounts of the Republic&apos;s assaults on the Falange, save for one instance, are pitiful and sickening. Descriptions, too, of Madrid during the conflict the likes of which I have not come across anywhere else. Exquisite and appalling. Read concurrently with Hugh Thomas&apos; <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/827971.The_Spanish_Civil_War' title='The Spanish Civil War by Hugh Thomas' rel='nofollow noopener'>The Spanish Civil War</a>.</span>
  <span id="freeText15319210063574811891" style="display:none">A wonderful book full of the stink and horror of war. The accounts of the Republic's assaults on the Falange, save for one instance, are pitiful and sickening. Descriptions, too, of Madrid during the conflict the likes of which I have not come across anywhere else. Exquisite and appalling. Read concurrently with Hugh Thomas' <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/827971.The_Spanish_Civil_War" title="The Spanish Civil War by Hugh Thomas" rel="nofollow noopener">The Spanish Civil War</a>.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15319210063574811891" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


