		<td>
		    <b>
          <a title="Goodreads Librarians Group" class="actionLink" href="https://www.goodreads.com/topic/show/22146865-how-can-i-add-cover-to-an-addition-that-publisher-no-longer-seems-to-exi">Goodreads Librari...:</a>
        </b>
      
			<a class="actionLink" href="/topic/show/22146865-how-can-i-add-cover-to-an-addition-that-publisher-no-longer-seems-to-exi">How can I add cover to an addition that publisher no longer seems to exist?</a>
		</td>
		<td class="nobreak">
		  9
		  
